; WINPCP.DEF - module definition for Windows 3.x display driver

NAME    WINPCP
DESCRIPTION 'Plantronics Color Plus display driver (640x200x4)'

; Windows display drivers are NE modules with a fixed export set.
; We'll align ordinals to match CGA/TANDY where practical.

EXPORTS
    ; Core lifecycle
    Enable          @1
    Disable         @2
    Inquire         @3
    Control         @4
    DeviceMode      @5

    ; Drawing (stubs initially)
    BitBlt          @6
    PatBlt          @7
    Pixel           @8
    LineTo          @9
    ScanLR          @10

    ; Text
    StrBlt          @11
    ExtTextOut      @14

    ; Cursor (names may vary; adjust once we lock the exact set)
    SetCursor       @15
    MoveCursor      @16
    CheckCursor     @17
